author: KEXP
description: Legendary Zamrock outfit @witch-weintendtocausehavoc hit the KEXP Gathering Space with a joyful, fuzz-soaked set of Zambian folk. Live on KEXP they share an energized performance of  "Kamusale" and more across their discography.
title: WITCH performs "Kamusale" & more Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents WITCH performing live in the KEXP gathering space. Recorded September 8, 2025

Songs:
Kamusale 01:08
Thou Shalt Not Cry 05:12
Queenless King 12:27
Toloka 18:03

Jagari Chandra - Vox
